I have incorporated the newest launch to the L’Oreal Paris Crystal Range, the Crystal Gel Cream and I’ve been using it religiously ever since! Powered by Salicylic acid, this cream goes 10 layers deep, refines pores and mildly exfoliates the skin leaving behind Crystal Clear Skin. I love the lightweight texture that absorbs quickly into the skin leaving behind no sticky residue. I highly recommend you guys adding this to your morning and night skincare routine!
